Embro II assumed the throne of the High King in the {{YearlinkName|614}}, following the death of his father.

During his reign, he managed to establish a temporary peace with his [[Northmen]] rivals.{{Cite dragon/362/Grand History of the Realms: The Moonshaes|27}}

Embro II ruled for eighteen years before being killed in battle by King [[Stromm]] of [[Norland]] in the {{YearlinkName|749}}.
